						<div class="postbody">You just mean that the map doesn't scroll, so both players can share the same map data at all times.<br /><br />From your description, I'm presuming F-Zero is very different than this, scrolling the map with wrapping. The wrapping makes it really hard to share, since you always need to keep the scrolling seam behind the player. Since there can only be one scrolling seam on a layer, only one player.</div>

